{"tid":2380504,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"舒適堡、Goji健身室數店遭入禀追租　Pure裁員　300中小店已結業","createTime":"2021-01-26T02:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T11:48:26.000Z","uid":1734,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"beb137586608adc9f85d68ac0ca99055466e8c6f","tid":2380504,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:41:47.000Z","msg":"本港新冠肺炎疫情反覆，健身中心於去年被政府勒令停業逾百日，再於12月第三度被勒令停業，至今重開無期。<br />\n《香港01》翻查法庭紀錄，發現大型健身中心舒適堡（Physical）及Goji Studios，近月均被業主入稟追討欠租，其中Goji Studios的旗下各分店於2020年，被業主入稟追租及申請封租令近20次，每次追討的金額均逾200萬元。另一大型健身中心Pure Fitness亦承認，因受疫情及停業令影響，近日裁減部份香港員工。<br />\n香港康樂體育專業人員總會會長李粵閩指，暫未見健身業界出現大規模裁員，但認為部份健身中心分店持續欠租，屬經營警號，望政府放寬健身教練採取適當的社交距離下，在戶外場地授課，及加快審批防疫抗疫基金下的健身中心資助計劃。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> goji 應該就快收皮"},{"pid":"8931f8fd4e837f8b988722e3de2783fd387cfc70","tid":2380504,"uid":261505,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"健身手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917c7fc1e6cbca1071eb373d9d57b7bba613ad9d","tid":2380504,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8931f8fd4e837f8b988722e3de2783fd387cfc70","tid":2380504,"uid":261505,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"健身手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"好彩physic